        <item>
            <title>Version 0.6.0</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>Density previews + resize smoothness</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Density preview now shows a real mini-terminal at each preset's actual padding — compact/cozy/spacious are visibly distinct</li>
                    <li>Resize is smooth: AppKit autoresizing drives SwiftTerm directly, no stale text on window drag</li>
                    <li>AI quick launch actually executes the command (sends CR, not LF)</li>
                    <li>Removed redundant cwd label from title strip</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
